org.sql: SELECT news.* FROM news INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = news.project_id WHERE news.created_on BETWEEN '2022-02-04' AND '2022-02-14' AND news.author_id = 2 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'news') IS NOT NULL
